item.title: Liu Feng
item.description: Self Introduction About me I work atAlibaba Group as a front-end developer,currently in Hangzhou,China. I am now working at TD, Transportation Division,backend system for ticket sales. If you are seeking any form of technology cooperation, please feel free to email me at yaoyuan.lf@alibaba-inc.com or yaoyuan.lf@gmail.com. I graduated from Computer Talent Class,Department of Computer Science, Anhui University (安徽大学计算机英才班) with a bachelor’s degree advised by Professor Zhang Lei.Subsequently, I commenced my Master’s studies in the Department of Mechanical Engineering at the University of Hong Kong.
